compilation_href.description: The HREF of the compilation used to create this execution

available_actions.description: Names of actions that can be run in the current state

available_operations.description: Names of operations that can be run in the current state

available_operations_info.description: The name and description of currently available operations

configuration_options.description: Configuration options initially provided to create execution

api_resources.description: Resources created by execution and defined in its CAT

outputs.description: Outputs created by execution and defined in its CAT

launched_from.description: How the CloudApp was launched, either from Application, Template, source, or compiled_cat

launched_from_summary.description: How the CloudApp was launched, either from Application, Template, source, or compiled_cat

deployment_url.description: URL of the CloudApp deployment in the Cloud Management Dashboard

scheduled.description: Indicates whether or not an execution has a scheduled start action

value.description: Amount of instance usage in CloudApp deployment, only available roughly 24 hours after launch, empty if not available

unit.description: Currency used for the cost value

ends_at.description: The time of the next 'terminate' ScheduledAction (if any).

schedule_required.description: Whether the CloudApp requires a schedule. If set to false, allows user to pick from '24/7' schedule in the UI

current_schedule.description: The currently selected schedule name, or nil for CloudApps using the '24/7' schedule

kind.description: The kind of this resource, always self_service#execution
